These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, prince, baccarat
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, engineer, firefighter
1. the oliveros-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the architect is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
3. the architect is the prince-smoker##1
4. the baccarat-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the engineer is the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Cigar   | baccarat | oliveros | prince |
| Job    | engineer    | firefighter | architect |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, bluemaster, game
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, roller, taxi
1. the chaman-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the roller is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the game-smoker##1
4. the person driving the roller is the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Cigar       | bluemaster | game | chaman |
| Transport   | taxi    | roller     | boat        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
House: colonial, tower, cottage
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, electronic, salsa
1. the colonial house is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the tower house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| House         | cottage     | tower | colonial |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep     | salsa  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, sports, superhero
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, green, azure
1. the person watching sports movies is the person who likes green##1
2. the person watching musical movies is the person who likes azure##1
3. the person watching sports movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | sports  | musical  |
| Color         | fuchsia  | green | azure |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, chess, gardening
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, animation, satire
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person watching fantasy movies##2
2. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | camping   | gardening | chess    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | satire     | fantasy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, chinese, german
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, lacrosse, tennis
1. the japanese is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the chinese##1
3. the chinese is in an odd position##4
4. the german is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Nationality   | chinese | german | japanese   |
| Sport   | tennis     | cricket    | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, horror, martial-arts
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, french, japanese
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is between the japanese and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the dutch is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | documentary | horror |
| Nationality           | french         | dutch         | japanese |

