.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, carrot, kale
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, amaryllis, iris
1. the person who growszinnia is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person eating artichoke##2
2. the person who growsiris is in an odd position##4
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | carrot | kale | artichoke |
| Flower    | amaryllis    | zinnia | iris     |

