.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, poker, go
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person playing poker##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Game   | go   | poker  | mah-jongg  |
| Sport         | tennis | lacrosse | climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, cola
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, drama, documentary
1. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is in an even position##4
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | 7up    | cola      | coffee |
| Movie-Genre       | drama | documentary | musical   |

