.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, collecting, photography
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, subway, trike
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person driving the trike is the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Hobby         | collecting | photography | writing |
| Transport   | subway | trike   | helicopter |

