.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, colombian, nigerian
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, aristoff, swisher
1. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
2. the australian is the swisher-smoker##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the colombian##3
4. the swisher-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality   | nigerian | colombian | australian |
| Cigar     | aristoff     | game   | swisher        |

