.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, bike, helicopter
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, sailing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Transport   | helicopter  | trike | bike   |
| Sport         | sailing | tennis   | cycling |

