.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, scooter, bike
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit
1. the person driving the bike is between the person driving the scooter and the owner of the pony##2
2. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person driving the bike is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Transport   | scooter | bike | taxi |
| Pet     | goldfish    | rabbit  | pony   |

 #################################

 
