.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, hamster, rat
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, funk, jazz
1. the fan of jazz is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is in the middle##1
3. the owner of the rat is the fan of funk##1
4. the fan of classical is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Pet         | rat | rabbit   | hamster |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | classical | jazz      |

