.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, water
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, handball, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person drinking water##1
3. the person drinking water is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Beverage     | milk  | water   | lemonade |
| Sport   | lacrosse | handball | golf       |

 